    "description": "Play board games in virtual reality as well as in non-VR mode.<br><br>Currently the following games are available to play:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Backgammon<br></li><li> Checkers<br></li><li> Tic-Tac-Toe<br></li><li> Chess</li></ul><br>The game of <strong><u>chess</u></strong> is only available in multiplayer, since its AI is still under development.<br>Check the game announcements for updates and more info: <br><br>You can configure the following using the <u>menu button</u> (on your controller or on the screen) to configure game settings:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>AI difficulty level<br></li><li>music volume<br></li><li>table height</li></ul><br>In the near future, you will be able to <strong><u>customize existing games</u></strong> as well as to <strong><u>make your own board games</u></strong> for you and the whole world to enjoy playing. This feature is currently under development.<br><br>Please note that you might need a chair to sit on when playing the game. In which case, try not to injure yourself.<br><br>Development of this game started as a hobby project to chill and play backgammon. After a while I decided to put all my time into it, expand it and share the game and its experience with the world.<br><br>I hope you will enjoy the game!<br><br>Share your constructive feedback here with me and watch them happen over time! Your feedback is valuable and appreciated.<br><br>❤️❤️❤️",
